R/I
0+I \to 0
1+I \to 1
x+I \to a
1+x+I \to b
(R/I,+,\cdot)
\{1,a,b\}
1 \cdot 1 = 1
1 \cdot a = a
1 \cdot b = b
a \cdot a = b
(x + I)(x + I) = (x^2 + I) = x^2 + 2x + 2 + I = (x + 1) + (x^2 + x + 1) + I = x +1 + I
a \cdot b = 1
(x + I)(1 + x + I) = x^2 + x + I = x^2 + x + 2 + I = 1 + x^2 + x + 1 + I = 1 + I
b \cdot b = a
(x + 1 + I)(x + 1 + I) = x^2 + 2x + 1 + I = x + x^2 + x + 1 + I = x + I
1^{-1} = 1, a^{-1} = b, b^{-1} = a
